  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Miromatrix Medical has developed MIROMESH® - a new, noncrosslinked, acellular mesh derived
      from the highly vascularized porcine liver. MIROMESH received FDA 510(k) clearance with an
      indication for reinforcement of soft tissue on March 31, 2014 under K134033. This study will
      serve to provide clinicians with high-quality clinical data in order to provide them with a
      higher degree of confidence when selecting MIROMESH for hiatal hernia repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
